# ⭐ Pattern 2

## Output

```text
***
***
***
```

## Pseudocode

```text
START

FOR i = 1 TO 3

    FOR j = 1 TO 3

        OUTPUT "*" WITHOUT NEWLINE

    END FOR

    OUTPUT NEWLINE

END FOR

STOP
```

---

## Java Code

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i++) {

    for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j++) {

        System.out.print("*");

    }

    System.out.println();

}
```

