# ⭐ Pattern 5

## Output

```text
123
123
123
```

### Method 1 (Easy)

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i++) {

    System.out.println("123");

}
```

### Method 2 (Interview Method ✅)

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i++) {

    for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j++) {

        System.out.print(j);

    }

    System.out.println();

}
```

### Why Method 2?

Because it shows that you understand how nested loops generate the output instead of printing a fixed string.

