# 📚 Dry Run

Example

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= 2; i++) {

    for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j++) {

        System.out.print("*");

    }

    System.out.println();

}
```

### Iteration 1

```
i = 1

j = 1 → *

j = 2 → *

j = 3 → *

Output

***
```

### Iteration 2

```
i = 2

j = 1 → *

j = 2 → *

j = 3 → *

Output

***
```

Final Output

```text
***
***
```

