# ❌ Common Mistakes

### Mistake 1

```java
System.out.println(" ");
```

✅ Better

```java
System.out.println();
```

---

### Mistake 2

Printing a fixed string every time.

```java
System.out.print("123");
```

Better for interviews:

```java
System.out.print(j);
```

---

### Mistake 3

Forgetting the new line after the inner loop.

Wrong

```java
***
******
***
```

Correct

```text
***
***
***
```

